==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Desperately
<hw>Des"per*ate*ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In a desperate manner;
without regard to danger or safety; recklessly; extremely; <as>as, the
troops fought <ex>desperately</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>She fell <qex>desperately</qex> in love with him.</q>
<rj><qau>Addison.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Desperateness</ent>⟦br⟧
